snippet.title: Walkabout Mini Golf | Spring 2023 Update | Meta Quest 2 + 3 + Pro
snippet.description:
Get Walkabout Mini Golf: https://metaque.st/43obQrK

Walkabout Mini Golf—the best-rated multiplayer on the Meta Quest—unearths FOUR exciting new developments coming soon:

1) Walkabout Mini Golf: Journey to the Center of the Earth (out June 8). Grab your putter and flashlight as you traverse the network of caverns that lead you to a mushroom forest, brilliant gems, and an underground ocean occupied with living prehistoric creatures!
2) A totally new series called Evil Lairs with the first installment Walkabout Mini Golf: Laser Lair blowing up in July featuring…
3) a bonus Exploding Kittens foxhunt by Elan Lee. And
4) a glimpse at Pocket Edition for iOS with crossplay for Meta Quest coming late Summer! 

Website: www.walkaboutminigolf.com
